name: rebuild : csh21
description:
personal piece based on the 1959 photo by julius shulman of case study house 21, or stahl house, located in los angeles.

of the entire case study house program, as organized and publicized by arts and architecture magazine the the 1950's and 1960's, csh 21 remains the most recognized residence in large part due to mr. shulman's iconic photograph.

moving the photo and the house to another time and space, it is occupied, flooded and violated outside of its historical comfort zone.

and still, it stands firm

justin r wood | @antiquefuture

minted dec 8 2021
